title: Vox in the Box!
description:
PA is VOX in the Box at the X this morning for Wild morning skate!
Tenna B co-hosts the first hour.
Head Coach Bruce Boudreau stops by to chat!
The Athletic's Michael Russo joins, Anthony LaPanta, Alex Stalock and all things Wild hockey.
